comments.body: This is a dark-morph female ETS. Note the flattened forewing submarginal spots, more extensive blue on the hindwing, and the yellowish patches at the end of the forewing cell. Many examples here: http://butterfliesofamerica.com/L/t/Pterourus_g_glaucus_a.htm

results.place_guess: Lake Shore Ave, Minnetonka, MN 55345, USA
